Content:: Aleksandr Svyatoslavovich Riabushenko (Belarusian: Аляксандр Святаслававіч Рабушэнка; born 12 October 1995) is a Belarusian cyclist, who currently rides for UCI WorldTeam Astana Qazaqstan Team.[5] In October 2020, he was named in the startlist for the 2020 Vuelta a España.[6] His father, Svyatoslav Ryabushenko, also competed professionally as a cyclist.[7] Former riders: list of riders
